description: Update ``aws opsworks`` model to the latest version
Fix issue with ``--max-items`` with ``aws route53``, ``aws iam``, and ``aws ses`` (`issue 729 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/pull/729>`__)
Fix issue with fips-us-gov-west-1 endpoint (`issue botocore 265 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/265>`__)
Fix issue when displaying unicode characters in table output (`issue 721 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/pull/721>`__)
Fix regression when syncing files with whitespace (`issue 706 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/706>`__, `issue 718 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/718>`__)
